member.name: P:InterviewSummary.ReusableHTML.AutomaticUpdate
member.summary: If this option is selected, the content of this list item will be inserted into web pages as a read-only reference. New versions of this item will automatically appear in the web pages. If the option is not selected, the content of this list item will be inserted into web pages as a copy that page authors can then modify. New versions of this item will not appear in the web pages. Any change to this setting will not affect existing web pages that are using this item.
